Any amount given in a currency other than the local currency is indicative
and not contractual.

Special terms
If a Stay Plus complimentary night is used, it will not include the daily
inclusions associated with this offer.

Children Policy
Accommodation and buffet breakfast are free for one child under the age of
12 staying and sharing in their parents' or grandparents' room.

Check in Policy
